data.description: Welcome to this 3/2 home with a 2 car garage and fenced back yard available in "Porter Shores" that has been completely freshly painted inside. The open concept floor plan seamlessly connects the living, dining and kitchen areas, providing an inviting space for family gatherings and entertaining guests. The fenced in back yard allows overflow of guests as you barbeque on your covered patio.  The master suite has a walk in closet and master bath boasts a garden tub as well as an oversized a walk in shower.  This home has a newer AC unit and sensi programmable thermostat.  But wait there is more- A mini split AC in the garage as well.  Newer well water pump and water softener system have been installed. Come take a look and give it your personal touches to make it your own.
